machine_description:
I see a number of items. There is (from left to right):
1. a balloon attached to a ribbon that is tied in a bow with a weight at the other end of it;
2. a device that looks like a mounted bow and arrow; 
3. a small rocket ship;
4. a hamster wheel with a hamster running on it, with a lever that looks like a foot underneath the wheel running on a balancing platform with a wheel underneath it; and
5. a device that is held up with a nail and plugged into an outlet with a cord with a saw at the end of it.

All of these items appear to be hand drawn in doodle format.
